---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-left">
        <p class="section-label">About Me</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          A developer who<br /><em>doesn’t stop learning</em>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="about-right">
        <p class="lead">
          I'm a software developer with 5 years of experience building web
          applications. I balance a strong frontend toolkit — Angular, React,
          TypeScript — with hands-on Node backend, testing, and CI/CD
          experience. I care about real-world quality, maintainability, and
          getting things done with intent.
        </p>
        <p>
          I’ve built features end-to-end: from architecture and API integration
          to delivery and optimization. Outside of work, I enjoy deep-diving
          into tech conversations with friends, sharpening my mind with puzzles,
          and building LEGO sets one brick at a time.
        </p>
        <!-- <p>
          Basically I’m someone who constantly keeps learning with a growth
          mindset, picks up frameworks and languages quickly, and with the right
          guidance gets the job done efficiently.
        </p> -->
        <div class="about-quote">
          <span class="quote-mark">"</span>
          <p>
            I don't just build features. I think about what they're for.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about {
    background: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--sand);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sand);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-left {
    position: sticky;
    top: 8rem;
  }

  .section-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
  }

  .about-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--charcoal-soft);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .about-quote {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--terracotta);
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    opacity: 0.2;
    position: absolute;
    top: -0.5rem;
    left: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    .about-left {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
